    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, offering a dependable driving experience for its next owner. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections and typical signs of wear consistent with its age, the overall mechanical health is solid. It has recently undergone a full inspection and is ready for the road without any immediate major repairs required.",
