    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with regular use, such as small paint chips, but has no major dents or rust. The interior is clean with light wear on the seats and all features are functional. The engine and transmission have been regularly maintained and the car runs reliably.",
